5A44590A.Line1.8DD12: Rathma did not know how Lilith may be freed from her prison. That knowledge is held by the Tree of Whispers.

F438D28C.Line3.8DD12: It demands a price: my head at my death. But who knows when that death will come. In all likelihood, too soon. But I will not be shackled. I will not be stopped.
